This paper involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques to generate commit messages, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). It also involves software engineering (cs.SE) as it deals with code changes and version control. The use of neural networks and preprocessing techniques also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of diff embeddings, which could potentially involve computer vision techniques (cs.CV).
